{
  "version": "style-sets-2026-06-08-gradient",
  "_doc": "Curated text style sets. Each set defines per-ROLE styling that fully owns the look of an overlay (the LLM/recipe supplies only text + timing + role). Every `font_family` MUST be a key in assets/fonts/font-registry.json; every `effect` must be in VALID_EFFECTS (app/agents/_schemas/template_text.py) plus the renderer-level karaoke-line/lyric-line; every `position` must be a key in _POSITION_Y (app/pipeline/text_overlay.py). Fields left null fall through to the LLM/legacy advisory value, then the renderer default. Design direction: editorial fonts (serif + one mono; no cheap geometric sans), restrained sizes (text_size_px ~38-88, consistent scale across agentic sets), thin strokes (rely on the renderer's gaussian shadow). See app/pipeline/style_sets.py. Editing this file changes STYLE_SETS_VERSION which is folded into the Layer-2 cache key.",
